One of the reasons
I'm going through this

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:08.120
is that we hope that in
the period of this course

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:09.650
you'll actually form some teams.

00:11:09.650 --> 00:11:12.424
So if you find some of
these topics interesting,

00:11:12.424 --> 00:11:13.840
or if you're some
of these people,

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:16.112
then at least I'm
shouting you out a bit.

