00:14:33.870 --> 00:14:39.450
If you over-deliver
on what you promise,

00:14:39.450 --> 00:14:41.510
you'll have people happy--
your investors will

00:14:41.510 --> 00:14:43.410
be happy, your customers.

00:14:43.410 --> 00:14:47.360
So happiness is reality
divided by expectation,

00:14:47.360 --> 00:14:51.920
with the fact that you can never
quite get expectations to zero.

00:14:51.920 --> 00:14:55.250
So lower your expectations--
I want you to all be happy

