00:59:49.000 --> 00:59:51.270
And we'll get
Steve to get stuff,

00:59:51.270 --> 00:59:53.480
who's going to tell you
how to make a pitch.

00:59:53.480 --> 00:59:55.870
So at the end of the day,
after everything you've done,

00:59:55.870 --> 00:59:57.495
you've got to come
and make that pitch.

00:59:57.495 --> 01:00:00.030
And Steve is going to give
